snippet.title: Actua Soccer Club edition gameplay (PC Game, 1996)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Actua Soccer Club edition, Dos PC game produced by Gremlin Interactive in 1996 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/actua-soccer-club-edition/2126/
Picking Mancherster UTD and playing the first matches of the season. Loosing 0-1 against Liverpool.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
